CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper April 5, 1958, pg. A6, reads: "Youth Concert Soloists - These five young people were soloists at the youth concert, presented by the Pittsburgh Concert Society, March 29, at Stephen Foster Memorial. Left to right: Jacqueline Vacco, pianist; Carol Titus, pianist; Ella L. Wilson, soprano; William Garbey, baritone, and Patricia Hummel, pianist, - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Concert Society Youth Concert soloists: pianist Jacqueline Vacco, pianist Carol Titus, soprano Ella L. Wilson, baritone William Garbey, and pianist Patricia Hummel, gathered around piano in Stephen Foster Memorial Hall
